#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-chain-building.md:44
msgid ""
"Once the chain is valid, fill in any required inputs in the dynamic form and "
"click **Execute**. The execution panel shows per-step progress, intermediate "
"results, timing, and the final combined output."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-chain-building.md:48
