msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-chain-building.md:50
msgid ""
"A completed chain can be exported as a **JSON** configuration file or as a "
"**BPMN 2.0** diagram for import into an Operaton process definition."
msgstr ""

